title: Brass Jack Puzzle
description:
The Jack Puzzle is made up of six different notched brass bars that interlock in one specific way to create a unified "jack" shape. It is exactingly milled, and weighs just over one pound. A desk object, a paperweight, and a true distraction — but be warned, if you take it apart, you might not be able to figure out how to put it back together. Includes assembly instructions.

  • Dimensions: 3 x 3 x 3 in.
  • 1.1 lbs
  • Solid brass, .5 in diameter rods, bull-nose ends, lathe-cut
